77
00:04:03,569 --> 00:04:08,268
couldn't change
the orientation of this aircraft.

78
00:04:08,269 --> 00:04:12,478
And an attitude control system,
like a spaceship, had to be used.

79
00:04:12,509 --> 00:04:14,989
It's a very remarkable project;

80
00:04:16,084 --> 00:04:18,293
to think that in the 60s,
they already reached

81
00:04:18,293 --> 00:04:22,493
these very high velocities in space
