118
00:06:25,474 --> 00:06:29,210
that was quite a challenge
to provide this change in the geometry

119
00:06:29,211 --> 00:06:30,930
for the re-entry in the atmosphere.

120
00:06:30,931 --> 00:06:33,390
Quite a successful program.

121
00:06:33,391 --> 00:06:37,931
And this team won
